Version 0.2

 - Add TESTSH_LOGGING variable; if set to '1', each test outputs to its own log
   file so you can see the results of each test.
 - Add optional _testsh_pre_test and _testsh_post_test functions

 - Change variable 'base_name' to 'testbasename'
 - Change variable 'tmpdir' to 'testtmpdir'

 - Fix building, linting
 - Fix TESTSH_SRCDIR to point to the right place
